<br>
Anyhow, I've gotten to a point where I don't know what to do with my gear.  I have too much WIS, and would like to get rid of some and replace it with AC/HP.  I have decent resistances so I'm not worried about them too much.<br>
<br>
Thanks!<br>
<br>
My equiment is as follows...<br>
<font face='courier new'><br>
Primary:    Nature Walker's Scimitar<br>
Secondary:  Sarnak Battle Shield<br>
