<br>
Fingerbone Hoop for Earring of Essence slot, use Essence for MR situations sorta deal. 2ac 5sta *which is 15hp on us small folks* 5str 5mr 5cr 5fr and some neg dr pr and cha, Effect : See Invis.<br>
<br>
Paebla Fetish or Talisman of Benevolence over Othmir Totem. Fetish's are quite common in its area of drop and quite a fun camp-or rather challenging which = fun :p<br>
Anyhow Fetish is 7ac 9wis 5str 5 all resists 15mana, Talisman is 7ac 12wis 12MR 12 CR 55mana 38hp<br>
<br>
Get a Bracer of Hammerfal over one of your Verm bracers, they are very simple to get for the stats involved which are 6ac 5sta 25hp 3wis and effect:summon hammers. Thats 1ac and 40hp total over a Verm bracer.<br>
<br>
Well anyhow those are some of the simpler suggestions. <p><center>
